<i>Olha, vês?</i>

00:30:29.213 --> 00:30:30.047 line:95%
CRIANÇA MORRE

00:30:30.130 --> 00:30:31.088 line:95%
<i>Vês?</i>

00:30:31.672 --> 00:30:33.338 line:95%
<i>Este és tu,</i>
<i>se saíres de casa.</i>

00:30:34.338 --> 00:30:37.172 line:95%
